interaxon inc private company information  bloomberg july    am et software company overview of interaxon inc snapshot people company overview interaxon inc designs and develops brainwavecontrolled products and experiences to help users from physical emotional and mental obstacles the company specializes in thought controlled computing solutions its technology is a software and hardware interface that enables the users to control various solutions using the mind by converting brainwaves into digital signals that are fed into a computer the company offers muse headband a sensory headband that is designed to help users meditate by providing realtime audio and visual feedback on meditative state through the muse companion application interaxon inc was founded in  and is based in toronto canada  king street westsuite toronto on mv kcanadafounded in  phone  wwwchoosemusecom key executives for interaxon inc mr  derek chief executive officer ms ariel garten founder and chief evangelist officer mr trevor coleman founder mr chris aimone founder and chief technical officer prof steve mann founder and scientific advisor to chief executive officer compensation as of fiscal year  interaxon inc key developments safilo group and interaxon inc announce strategic research and development partnership and licensing agreement dec   safilo group and interaxon inc announced a strategic research and development partnership and licensing agreement this partnership enables safilos entry into wearable technology under the name of safilox ™ interaxon and safilo have been exploring their first eyewear developments in undisclosed work over the past  months to develop this eyewear platform the partner companies have established a team of experts devoted to the seamless integration of invisible brain sensing technology with stylish product design development and engineering resulting in technology that is invisible to the user but with a relevant functionality and aspirationally styled design sim